  <brief_title>B-type Natriuretic Peptide as a Surrogate Marker Guiding Post-operative Fluid Off-loading</brief_title>
  <official_title>B-type Natriuretic Peptide (BNP) as a Surrogate Marker Guiding Post-operative Fluid Off-loading</official_title>
